f \in c_0^*
||f||=\sum_{j=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{j!}
\begin{eqnarray} f: c_0 & \to & \mathbb{R}\\   (x_i)_1^{\infty} & \to & \displaystyle \sum_{j=1}^{\infty} \frac{x_j}{j!}\\ \end{eqnarray}
f \in c_0^*
